text: Abramovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kosinskoye Rural Settlement of Kosinsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 66 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == The village is located 2 km west from Kosa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kosinsky District
title: Abramovo, Perm Krai
